# Popularized by: Ernesto Lecuona (classical), Sabicas, Paco de Lucia (flamenco)

# Harmony Reference
# Key: E Phrygian (E-F-G-A-B-C-D)
# Typical chords: E(i) - F(II) - Am(iv)
# Cadence: Am - G - F - E (Andalusian)
# Left-hand: E major chord forms with embellishments

# Technique Reference
# Right-hand: Rasgueado (rolling strum), tremolo, arpeggio, golpes
# Character: Free rubato, expressive descending lines, showcase piece

